RestAssured documentation

1. Create a Maven project

2. Add the following dependencies to the POM.xml file
rest-assured
testng

Optional to add also:
JsonPath
XmlPath
JSON Schema Validation

API to use
https://reqres.in/



3. Keywords used in BDD

given()-set cookies ,  add authentication , add parameters , set headers info etc...

when()-get, post , put , delete - the actual call

then()- validation status code , extract response , extract headers cookies & response body...



4. Validations:

Status Code

Status Line

Response Body

header